Homepage: http://code.google.com/p/linux-whiteboard

Package: whiteboard
Architecture: i386
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Turns a normal screen to a touch screen using the wiimote.
 This program allows controlling the mouse cursor with an infrared pen using
 the Wiimote, effectively transforming any type of screen (including those
 generated by projectors) to touch panel. It makes use of Johnny Lee's idea,
 visit his projects's homepage at: http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~johnny/projects/wii/ .
 .


